msgctxt "#32046"
msgid "Update, regenrate VPN WireGuard config files."
msgstr "Update, regenrate VPN WireGuard config files."

msgctxt "#32047"
msgid "Pick a WireGuard file from any folder. The addon automatically copies and renames it to custom_[country].config, then updates the internal name so the VPN matches your menu and folder mapping. The addon gets the country directly from the original filename you select. For example, if you pick a file named belgium.conf, the script strips the extension and uses \"Belgium\" to rename the file and set the internal connection name."
msgstr "Pick a WireGuard file from any folder. The addon automatically copies and renames it to custom_[country].config, then updates the internal name so the VPN matches your menu and folder mapping. The addon gets the country directly from the original filename you select. For example, if you pick a file named belgium.conf, the script strips the extension and uses \"Belgium\" to rename the file and set the internal connection name."

msgctxt "#32048"
msgid "Import Username/Password. Select a txt file containing your PIA credentials."
msgstr "Import Username/Password. Select a txt file containing your PIA credentials."

msgctxt "#32049"
msgid "File Format for Import: ¦ Line 1: Your Username (e.g., p1234567). ¦ Line 2: Your Password (e.g., MySecretPass) ¦ Make sure there are no extra spaces or empty lines in the text file."
msgstr "File Format for Import: ¦ Line 1: Your Username (e.g., p1234567). ¦ Line 2: Your Password (e.g., MySecretPass) ¦ Make sure there are no extra spaces or empty lines in the text file."

